item.title: Varrock teleport
item.dc:creator: @dirtynife dirtynife
item.description:
@dirtynife wrote:

  1. Go in your game and type ::mypos and get those cords.
  2. Go to clickingMost.java and do ctrl+F to open up the find thingy.
  3. Type in the cords you got. Xâ€™s cords would be sufficient.
  4. Change those cords with the cords of the place you want it to teleport you to.
  5. Go to texthandler.java and do ctrl+F and type in the current name of teleport.
  6. Change it with the name you want it to be.
  7. Your done. Enjoy.
